{"tid":2318043,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"羅志祥復出前夕頻出事 周揚青12字暗酸舊愛","createTime":"2020-12-09T04:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T04:53:08.000Z","uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4243000c142cf2c7e3775ed70729220e645098bd","tid":2318043,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T04:53:08.000Z","msg":"沉寂８個月後，羅志祥宣布明年將帶著音樂作品復出，豈料卻又爆出他在內湖豪宅頂樓違建蓋泳池，復出之路相當不順。相較於小豬，周揚青恢復單身後，事業運大開，經營的網拍事業蒸蒸日上<br />\n<br />\n。。。。<br />\n<br />\n周揚青昨日在微博透露有東西不見，有感而發地寫道：「當你丟了東西心情不好的時候，去買一個和丟的一模一樣的東西騙自己沒丟，心情就變好了。這還是幾年前我媽教我的，但這前提是你要努力賺錢。」引起網友共鳴，紛紛留言笑稱「只有錢才能帶來安全感」<br />\n<br />\n。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vaLyGdF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvaLyGdF.png&h=cbf6d6f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A6cJi0m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6cJi0m.png&h=700f3d22&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RG97LFm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRG97LFm.png&h=c4895ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201209/UH4NXEMRLNBMPLCJQE23I25DZI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201209%2FUH4NXEMRLNBMPLCJQE23I25DZI%2F&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUBAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=526732d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201209%2FUH4NXEMRLNBMPLCJQE23I25DZI%2F&h=f9566ca4\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201209/UH4NXEMRLNBMPLCJQE23I25DZI/</a>"}]}